[Help] Nikon transfer program no longer recognizing my external hard drives? /!/ I prefer using the View NX2 program to transfer my photos (as opposed to Lightroom or anything else) but for some reason it's suddenly not recognizing my external hard drives when I try to transfer from the camera to my HDs. I can see the hard drives on View but can't find them with the Transfer function. I've uninstalled and then reinstalled the program but I'm still having problems. When I click to browse to find my destination, the only options it gives me are "desktop" and my user file, there are no options for "Computer" or various drives.

What is going on?
